---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Banner Header -->
  <div class="banner-header section-padding valign bg-img bg-fixed" data-overlay-dark="4" data-background="img/slider/04.jpg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2 text-center caption mt-90">
          <h5 class="animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeInUp">
            <a href="index.html">Home</a> / Tax Services
          </h5>
          <h1 class="animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeInUp">Tax Services</h1>
          <hr class="animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeInUp">
          <p class="animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeInUp">
            Your trusted partner in tax planning and return preparation
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tax Services Content Section -->
  <div class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 mt-15">
          <p>
            By keeping current on new tax laws and legislation, we are in a position to identify key tax planning opportunities that minimize both your current and future tax liabilities. We provide our individual and business clients with the taxation expertise and knowledge that they deserve throughout the year.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Tax services offered include but are not limited to:</strong>
          </p>
          <p><strong>Tax planning &amp; return preparation</strong></p>
          <!-- Unordered list with descriptions -->
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Individuals:</strong> Receive personalized tax solutions that maximize benefits and ensure accuracy.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Corporations:</strong> Benefit from comprehensive tax management designed for compliance and substantial savings.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Partnerships:</strong> Navigate complex partnership tax issues with tailored, strategic guidance.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>LLCs/LLPs:</strong> Get expert advice that optimizes tax outcomes and effectively manages liabilities.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Estates, trusts &amp; gift:</strong> Handle estate planning, trust administration, and gift strategies with specialized expertise.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Sales Taxes:</strong> Ensure accurate computation and timely compliance with sales tax obligations.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Payroll Taxes:</strong> Streamline payroll processes to keep your workforce compliant and operations efficient.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            If you'd like to learn more about our services, please <a href="contact.html">contact us</a> for a free consultation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
